translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  31,20,"Kya tumlog nahin dekhte ke Allah ne zameen aur aasmaano ki saari cheezein tumhare liye musakkhar kar rakkhi hai aur apni khuli aur chupi niyamatein tumpar tamaam kardi hain? Ispar haal yeh hai ke Insano mein se kuch log hain jo Allah ke barey mein jhagadte hain bagair iske ke unke paas koi ilm ho, ya hidayat, ya koi roshni dikhane wali kitaab"
  31,21,Aur jab unsey kaha jaata hai ke pairwi karo us cheez ki jo Allah ne nazil ki hai to kehte hain ke hum to us cheez ki pairwi karenge jispar humne apne baap dada ko paya hai. Kya yeh unhi ki pairvi karenge khwah shaytan unko bhadakti hui aag hi ki taraf kyun na bulata raha ho
  31,22,"Jo shaks apne aap ko Allah ke hawale karde aur amalan woh neik ho, usne fil-waqayi ek bharose ke qabil sahara thaam liya, aur saarey maamlaat ka aakhri faisla Allah hi ke haath hai"
  31,23,"Ab jo kufr karta hai uska kufr tumhein gham mein mubtala na karey. Unhein palat kar aana to hamari hi taraf hai, phir hum unhein bata denge ke woh kya kuch karke aaye hain. Yaqeenan Allah seeno(chest) ke chupe huey raaz tak jaanta hai"
  31,24,"Hum thodi muddat unhein duniya mein mazey karne ka mauqa de rahey hain, phir unko bebas karke ek sakht azaab ki taraf kheench le jayenge"
  31,25,"Agar tum insey pucho ke zameen aur aasmaano ko kisne paida kya hai, to yeh zaroor kahenge ke Allah ne. Kaho alhamdulillah, magar inmein se aksar log jaante nahin hain"
  31,26,Aasmaano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai Allah hi ka hai. Beshak Allah be-niyaz (free of need) aur aap se aap mehmood (praiseworthy) hai
  31,27,Zameen mein jitne darakht hain agar woh sab ke sab qalam ban jayein aur samandar (dwaat (ink) ban jaaye) jisey saat (seven) mazeed samandar roshnayi(ink) muhayya karein tab bhi Allah ki baatein (likhne se) khatam na hongi. Beshak Allah zabardast aur hakeem hai
  31,28,Tum sarey Insano ko paida karna aur phir dobara jila uthana (zinda karna) to (uske liye) bas aisa hai jaise ek mutanaffis (single person) ko (paida karna aur jila uthana). Haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah sabkuch sunne aur dekhne wala hai